00:11:24,022 --> 00:11:26,523
There isn't one.
And that's the fourth-- ah!

243
00:11:26,558 --> 00:11:28,325
This one's an A.

244
00:11:28,359 --> 00:11:30,460
Are there really
two sides to this story?

