00:11:30,495 --> 00:11:33,664
So it's I-I-I-A.

246
00:11:33,698 --> 00:11:35,633
What does that mean,
are there really--

247
00:11:35,667 --> 00:11:39,369
The media is biased towards success and
the media is biased towards fairness.

248
00:11:39,404 --> 00:11:41,038
How can you be biased
toward fairness?

249
00:11:41,072 --> 00:11:42,639
There aren't two sides
to every story.

250
00:11:42,674 --> 00:11:45,309
Some stories have five sides,
